text: Hi <@U3T21PDBK>, It's just that one table.

Hey everyone, does anyone know if you can import data into a custom module in HubSpot? I have created a module for references and have to maintain 600 references there. I do not have the version with the HubDB

A response I received from HS support:

Hi Huanling,
The product team have returned on this and advised a fix has been applied.
What was happening is that there are some internal scopes (not visible to you) applied to external scopes.
As part of a recent update, the get custom object endpoint required a specific internal scope for the call.
The team updated the external scopes to correctly have this scope going forward, so you shouldn’t see an error any further with only the read/write scopes!
I’ll close out this ticket as this is now resolved, but if you have any follow up questions on this please let me know!
